com.serena.dmclient.objects
Class ImplicitStateCode

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.ImplicitStateCode

public class ImplicitStateCode
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates predefined implicit state shortcut codes used by item baseline template rules only that do not require a normal lifecycle state to be specified.

See Also:
BaselineTemplateRule.getLifecycleStatus(), BaselineTemplateRuleDetails.getLifecycleStatus()
